Farm and Fleet is committed to selling quality products at fair and honest prices. We strive to inspire and empower our customers to fulfill the needs of their work, home and active lifestyle with our unique mix of products and services.

• Browse, shop, and checkout—safe and easy ordering from anywhere with great savings.

• Search items by barcode for product and pricing information.

• Create, manage, and shop gift registries. Search, browse or use the app’s barcode scanner in store to add items.

• Use Shop on the Spot™ in your car to make a list and purchase at Drive-Thru without ordering ahead.

• Advance Order and pick up large or heavy purchases at your local store’s Drive-Thru without leaving your vehicle.

• Manage your account, view recent orders, review and change your local store with a few easy finger taps.

• Get notifications when your orders are shipped, delivered, or ready for pickup.

This app requires certain permissions to give you the best shopping experience and greatest feature set.

Farm and Fleet is committed to selling quality products at fair and honest prices. We strive to inspire and empower our customers to fulfill the needs of their work, home and active lifestyle with our unique mix of products and services.

• Browse, shop, and checkout—safe and easy ordering from anywhere with great savings.

• Search items by barcode for product and pricing information.

• Create, manage, and shop gift registries. Search, browse or use the app’s barcode scanner in store to add items.

• Use Shop on the Spot™ in your car to make a list and purchase at Drive-Thru without ordering ahead.

• Advance Order and pick up large or heavy purchases at your local store’s Drive-Thru without leaving your vehicle.

• Manage your account, view recent orders, review and change your local store with a few easy finger taps.

• Get notifications when your orders are shipped, delivered, or ready for pickup.

Important note about app permissions:
This app requires certain permissions to give you the best shopping experience and greatest feature set.

• Browse, shop, and checkout—safe and easy ordering from anywhere with great savings.

• Search items by barcode for product and pricing information.

• Create, manage, and shop gift registries. Search, browse or use the app’s barcode scanner in store to add items.

• Use Shop on the Spot™ in your car to make a list and purchase at Drive-Thru without ordering ahead.

• Advance Order and pick up large or heavy purchases at your local store’s Drive-Thru without leaving your vehicle.

• Manage your account, view recent orders, review and change your local store with a few easy finger taps.

• Get notifications when your orders are shipped, delivered, or ready for pickup.

Important note about app permissions:
This app requires certain permissions to give you the best shopping experience and greatest feature set.
